docs.title: Home
docs.text:
# Welcome

Welcome to the documentation for the `amtest24/test` repository.

Local preview:
- python -m venv .venv
- source .venv/bin/activate
- pip install -r requirements.txt
- mkdocs serve

docs.title: Getting Started
docs.text:
1. Create a branch (e.g., docs/init).
  2. Edit files under docs/ or mkdocs.yml.
  3. Run mkdocs build --strict locally to validate.
  4. Open a PR and merge to main to deploy via GitHub Actions.
